name: X. Time
description:
We understood that it was time for another dimension that should be acquired. Space is already ours. But time - unfortunately - is rushing forward inexorably. How to possess such a fleeting phenomenon?
And at this moment, my friend, here comes yout part. We needed a proxy. Thoroughly described all key moments of our civilization. A way to register our entire journey, all the time we existed, placed in one place.
You hold it in your hands. Thanks to you, whoever you are, we exist in each moment at the same time. Our whole history is repeated forever. Each time in a different speed and position. While you hold the phone in your hands.

So, what is the fifth dimension?
